decks.notes: The main idea behind this aggressive deck is to overwhelm the opponent with a fast and efficient creature-based strategy. By utilizing powerful creatures like Gruul Spellbreaker, Tarmogoyf, and Questing Beast, along with cards like Winota, Joiner of Forces and Fires of Invention, the deck aims to put pressure on the opponent early and close out the game quickly. The deck also includes disruptive creatures like Thalia, Guardian of Thraben and Gaddock Teeg to disrupt the opponent's game plan. With a mix of ramp and card advantage from cards like Birds of Paradise and Dark Confidant, the deck seeks to keep up the pressure and outpace the opponent in a fast-paced Duel Commander 1 vs 1 format.
